    Summary:
    X-link: https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/83760
    Approved by: https://github.com/zou3519

    Reviewed By: izaitsevfb

    Differential Revision: D39339969

    Pulled By: samdow

    fbshipit-source-id: 1b1e4e6f5ddaead36018103d8d2e76527a89ff1d
